Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 她果然在生我氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.03,0:00:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 恐怖得像惡鬼一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說要離家出走不再理她 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她竟然說有本事就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像跟我針鋒相對似的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼帶著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個我睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條毛巾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個也睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對安眠有多大渴求啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來想一想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離家出走是行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.41,0:00:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也總不能不上學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 這話輪到你說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.27,0:00:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂學校 只要休息一天就會出麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.98,0:00:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的第一步走得很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得休息那麼一天不會有什麼改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 覺得沒什麼改變就一天接一天地休息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回過神來發覺自己已經深陷於泥濘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我能以一副了不起的樣子說出這話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:00:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:00:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海真厲害 沒有浪費家裡蹲的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然宿海一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使自己身處劣境 也總是為別人考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是那樣顧慮著別人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.19,0:01:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面小芽比我比我強多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.41,0:01:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟雪集交談過 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說我們一直被小芽束縛著 這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣說 她現在還住在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 那樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.74,0:01:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是相信小芽的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:01:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買可爾必思牛奶回來了 小鳴 盛惠520日元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爾必思牛奶撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來看日記的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的可爾必思牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.79,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本字幕由天使字幕組製作 僅功學習交流之用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.79,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請於下載24小時後刪除 如喜歡本作品請支持正版
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.79,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻譯:夢の旅人 後期.校正:依戀緋鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:00:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了這個也許就能知道小芽的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我翻開了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽不為我所知的一面就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽不為我所知的想法就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:23.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（2月12日 陰天）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:23.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天跟大家一起玩 很有趣）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:31.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（2月14日 晴）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:31.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天跟大家一起玩 很高興）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有趣就是高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本無從下手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.56,0:04:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢夥從前就不太會寫文章啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這篇不是有點不同嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在跟大家玩耍的時候摔了一跤 好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這篇也不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家一起去探望仁太媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探病嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我們經常去的啊 大家一個跟著一個的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太的媽媽 一直都住在醫院裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 給神寄一封信吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容是仁太的媽媽早日康復
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼寄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家決定一起做一個煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得很難  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把信放在火箭煙花裡 然後寄給神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 願望是否就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 一定是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時說好要做最後卻不了了之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚歸的仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不良的仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外宿的仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太什麼的 人家才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半夜吃東西會變肥豬的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要變肥豬的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹽拉麵 還是有雞蛋湯的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有小健拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想弄些吃的給你 讓你高興一下而至
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸快回來了 你快點吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我明天也會上學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…你別跟來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不要再做奇怪的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 為什麼不上學卻穿著校服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿什麼是我的自由…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要使用煙花火藥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據火藥取締法 需要18歲以上並獲得國家資格才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具煙花的話 也許有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那也需要許可證
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來想 放煙花當然要獲得許可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.95,0:08:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 說起來 我昨天打掃的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集大量的煙花 把火藥拆散出來 然後把大家的彙集到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後放進廁紙的捲筒裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會燒起來所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼稚 真幼稚的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在以前 我們卻認為這行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 以前的我們 即使是這樣  也相信這真的能飛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信比夏天祭典看到的飛得更高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生啊 看起來像個了不起的大叔 感覺無所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但感覺那時候更加了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 有方向性地尋找辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此 那怎麼可能辦得到 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼想都不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都做到這一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這不是你所說的小芽的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是一場徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說宿海同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟你那邊的小芽確認過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我不敢向本人確認
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間閃現眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直走在我們前面的宿海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及在他身後觀望的可憐的雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  為什麼不說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那傢夥沒叫我們到秘密基地集合的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天小芽好像不在場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.14,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽打電話來叫我出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天好像有什麼要商量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得想起來了 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為剛才宿海在這
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還忘記了一件重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽說要瞞著宿海秘密收集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽說這樣說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認識一個能夠製作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我工地有一位大叔在祭典裡擔任煙花師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 仁太 想造煙花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我為什麼也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有這種想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個人造嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 是跟小袋他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 那就拜託他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 仁太 仁太 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我無法走出那個叫康達爾的城市）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 我現在聯絡他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個話題下次再繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 即使是簡單的煙花也花費很大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錢的話要做還是能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 情況怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20萬?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼龐大的金額我從沒看過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒問題 一定有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很小鳴拼死打工的話一定行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 別擅自幫我決定好不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好 大家相互幫助嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 那個數額一周工作七天就能輕鬆極達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 我還沒說要做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.38,0:12:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡輸入金額
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是二手貨的價格 這裡是新貨的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡輸入差額嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我花費一個月才學會的技能你一下子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那耗時太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎觀臨…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面卻而完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了 下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 果然是傳聞中的傢夥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不上學了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 那不是一直不上學的傢夥嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊 那傢夥到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這反倒不錯啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢夥搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺這樣子 跟那時候沒什麼變化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 拿膠帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿…海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 小鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別這樣叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海去打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對煙花的事似乎是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要貢獻一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.15,0:14:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟宿海一起不務正業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想做的話我也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你能出來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快考試了 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是年級第四
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年級第二在說什麼啊 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著你走會很勞神的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁回來太晚了 不良
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太絕對有古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上馬上就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上馬上就出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又到今天寵物欄目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狗是母的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是仁太在做奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天介紹的小狗是小奧斯卡爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:42.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小奧斯卡爾 雌性 7歲）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:42.55,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（哈巴狗）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哈巴狗好可愛啊 皺紋好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是母的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請在名簿上簽字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 仁太綴學了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 為什麼這麼問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 問了唐突的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過他之前好像在打工
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在倒垃圾的時候看到他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太有把那些事全部告訴你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 有啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我家奉行自由意志 要做什麼都交由他自己把握
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不好 這不好 這不好...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.24,0:16:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小袋?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天不用輪班
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長好像很喜歡他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他晚上跟你一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 七點鐘到地盤工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:16:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 突然做這個負擔太重了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不過要掙錢的話幹體力活倒是最快的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭煙花真是燒錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽的…願望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多為自己著想一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那態度真令人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 還好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 雪集有聯絡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 時常有聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很在意仁太的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 仁太?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 仁太就是仁太嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也那樣叫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫仁太有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太…仁太…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了就到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢夥真賣力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太真是帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小芽不在為自己考慮的時候 一直都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太一直都為我考慮著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小心腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擅自改變照明燈的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風能吹動照明燈的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥啊 揮灑著閃亮汗水的仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多也要靠譜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分接近媽媽做的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上學辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯 不過有點開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢 意外地比家裡蹲要輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種活著的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.88,0:20:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說實際上怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是目前為止的我…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽也是 看到散發出活力的仁太 有種活著的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們帶來了定金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還差很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請您先用這些開工
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉 我無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心對城裡的官員走漏了口風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他生氣起來 喊我不要給高中生幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都這麼努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.70,0:21:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個官員是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接跟他說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是…本間家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太他們為了你付出很多的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很荒唐對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
